Refs: #31324

Despite by best escaping ability I could not escape the comma or the pipe character in a user snippet to have it as a choice

Here's a simple thing which did not work for me when trying to have a comma as part of a choice.

Escaping comma just gets ignored, while escpaing the pipe confused the snippet completely and I am not given a choice.
```json
{
	"Print to console": {
		"prefix": "log",
		"body": [
			"console.log(${1|not\\, not, five, 5, 1   23|});",
			"$1"
		],
		"description": "Log output to console"
	}
}
```

Example 2

```json
{
	"Print to console": {
		"prefix": "log",
		"body": [
			"console.log(${1|not\\, not, \\| five, 5, 1   23|});",
			"$1"
		],
		"description": "Log output to console"
	}
}
```
